\pc \bd 2\bd*\bd 7\bd*

\s Una uhodari leo wa kumfuata Yesu
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Una uhodari leo wa kumfuata \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , hata ukichekwa sana na kuteswa duniani? \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Una uhodari leo kuwa mtu wake Mungu? Ukiona haya sana, kisha utaona nini? \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mji unaonekana ukijengwa mlimani, hivyo na imani yetu inadhihirika sana. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ukipenda \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  na kuliko vitu vyote, unataka kumkiri, mbele ya wenzako huku. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Chuki au ’pendeleo kwako kitu bure tena, watafuta siku zote sifa zake \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  Kristo\bd*\bd . \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ujihoji nafsi yako ukitaka kuokoka! Uliekataa Mungu, tubu dhambi zako leo! \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Umsihi masamaha, akuokoe ’kati \bd*\bd Damu\bd*\bd ! Omba uhodari tena wa kumfuata \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd ! \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Uchague \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  leo, uwe mfuasi wake! Ukitwaa \bd*\bd Msalaba\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd utaipokea taji! \bd*
